rows.label: qst400101_msg0002
rows.name:
Hey, Rubirubi-san. You still have
that thing we talked about?

rows.label: qst400101_msg0003
rows.name:
Finally! Did you finally save
up the money to buy it, mo?

rows.label: qst400101_msg0004
rows.name: You know it! Let me see it!

rows.label: qst400101_msg0005
rows.name:
Rex, how did you suddenly get
so rich, mo? Did you salvage
some amazing treasure, mo?

rows.label: qst400101_msg0006
rows.name:
I've taken on a big job direct
from the Chairman. I got 100,000G
just from the advance payment!

rows.label: qst400101_msg0008
rows.name:
But I'll be going into
uncharted waters, so I want
to make sure I'm prepared.

rows.label: qst400101_msg0009
rows.name:
In that case, I'm sure that
accessory will protect you, mo.

rows.label: qst400101_msg0010
rows.name: Good luck on the job, mo!
